<!-- Services Overview -->
<section class="services-overview">
<div class="container">
<div class="services-intro">
<h2>Comprehensive Economic Analysis &amp; Valuation Services</h2>
<p>Skerritt Economics &amp; Consulting provides reliable economic analysis and business valuation services to the legal community. Our expertise spans forensic economics for personal injury and employment cases, business valuations for litigation and planning, and specialized consulting for complex economic issues.</p>
<p>We understand that each case presents unique challenges requiring tailored economic solutions. Whether you need damage calculations for a catastrophic injury case, business valuation for shareholder litigation, or economic analysis for employment disputes, we provide the rigorous methodology and clear communication your case demands.</p>
</div>
